## Expected Impact

| Scenario | Before | After |
|----------|--------|-------|
| CLI repo, cold cache | ~86 DSNs → ~190 HTTP requests, hangs | 0 DSNs from test/ (Change 2) |
| Monorepo, cold cache | N DSNs → 2N concurrent requests | Deduped + max 5 concurrent |
| API down | Hangs indefinitely | 15s timeout, partial results |

